'''ᱨᱟᱡᱩ ᱥᱨᱤᱵᱟᱥᱛᱚᱵᱽ''' (ᱡᱟᱱᱟᱢ '''ᱥᱚᱛᱭᱚ ᱯᱨᱚᱠᱟᱥ ᱥᱨᱤᱵᱟᱥᱛᱚᱵᱚ''' ᱒᱕ ᱰᱤᱥᱮᱢᱵᱚᱨ ᱑᱙᱖᱓), ᱢᱤᱻᱢᱤᱫ ᱚᱠᱛᱚ '''ᱜᱚᱡᱳᱫᱷᱚᱨ''' ᱢᱮᱱᱛᱮ ᱦᱚᱸ ᱠᱚ ᱢᱮᱛᱟᱭ ᱜᱮᱭᱟ ᱾ ᱱᱩᱭ ᱫᱚ ᱢᱤᱫ ᱥᱤᱧᱚᱛᱤᱭᱟ. ᱠᱟᱢᱮᱰᱤᱭᱟᱱ ᱠᱟᱱᱟ ᱾

==ᱟᱬᱜᱟᱛ ᱡᱤᱭᱚᱱ==
ᱨᱟᱡᱩ ᱫᱚ ᱒᱕ ᱰᱤᱥᱮᱢᱵᱚᱨ ᱑᱙᱖᱓,[[ᱠᱟᱱᱯᱩᱨ]] ᱨᱮ ᱡᱟᱱᱟᱢ ᱞᱮᱱᱟᱭ ᱾ ᱢᱤᱫ ᱨᱮᱸᱜᱮᱡ ᱚᱲᱟᱜ ᱨᱮ ᱾ ᱟᱡ ᱵᱟᱵᱟ ᱨᱚᱢᱮᱥ ᱪᱚᱱᱫᱽᱨᱚ ᱥᱨᱤᱵᱟᱥᱛᱚᱵᱚ ᱫᱚ ᱢᱤᱫ ᱚᱱᱚᱞᱤᱭᱟ. ᱛᱟᱦᱮᱸ ᱠᱟᱱᱟᱭ ᱟᱨ ᱩᱱᱤ ᱫᱚ ᱵᱟᱞᱟᱭ ᱠᱟᱠᱟ ᱢᱮᱱᱛᱮ ᱦᱟᱲ ᱠᱚ ᱵᱟᱰᱟᱭ ᱞᱮᱫᱮᱭᱟ ᱾ ᱜᱤᱫᱽᱨᱟ. ᱠᱷᱚᱱᱟᱜ ᱜᱮ ᱦᱚᱲᱟᱜ ᱟᱲᱟᱝ ᱠᱚᱭ ᱞᱟ.ᱭ ᱜᱟᱱ ᱠᱷᱟ.ᱛᱤᱨ ᱨᱟᱡᱩ ᱫᱚ ᱠᱟᱢᱮᱰᱤᱭᱟᱱ ᱵᱮᱱᱟᱜ ᱥᱟᱱᱟ ᱞᱮᱫᱮᱭᱟ ᱾

==Career==
Srivastav has performed in stage shows in India and abroad.<ref name="DHInstitute2009">{{Cite web|url=https://www.deccanherald.com/content/24575/an-institute-comedy-courtesy-raju.html|title=An institute of comedy, courtesy Raju Srivastav|date=2009-09-11|website=Deccan Herald|language=en|access-date=2019-11-03}}</ref> He also launched a series of audio cassettes and video CDs. He gained initial notice as an [[Amitabh Bachchan]] look-alike.

He started his career by doing small roles in Bollywood films. He had a part in the [[Rajshri Productions]] movie ''Maine Pyar Kiya''<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://indianexpress.com/article/entertainment/bollywood/maine-pyar-kiya-salman-khan-lesser-known-facts-trivia-5003692/|title=28 years of Maine Pyar Kiya: Eight lesser-known facts about the Salman Khan starrer|date=2017-12-29|website=The Indian Express|language=en-IN|access-date=2019-11-03}}</ref> and other small roles in various movies such as ''[[Baazigar]]'' and ''[[Bombay to Goa (2007 film)|Bombay to Goa]]''.<ref name="DHInstitute2009"/> He worked as an actor and comedian in the Bollywood movie ''[[Aamdani Atthanni Kharcha Rupaiya]]''.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.abplive.in/videos/big-b-praises-raju-srivastav-in-kbc-comedian-gets-emotional-783522|title=Big B praises Raju Srivastav in KBC, comedian gets emotional|date=2018-11-23|website=ABP Live|language=en-US|access-date=2019-11-03}}</ref>

He ventured into stand-up comedy with the talent show ''[[The Great Indian Laughter Challenge]]''<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.tellychakkar.com/tv/tv-news/comic-moments-comedian-kapil-sharma-ginni-chatrath-recep-181225|title=Comic moments in comedian Kapil Sharma-Ginni Chatrath reception|website=Tellychakkar.com|language=en|access-date=2019-11-03}}</ref> and finished as second runner-up, subsequently taking part in the spin-off, ''The Great Indian Laughter Challenge - Champions'', in which he won the title of "The King of Comedy".

Srivastav also participated in ''[[Bigg Boss (Hindi season 3)]]'', the Indian counterpart of the ''[[Big Brother (franchise)]]''. After staying in the house for more than two months he was voted out on December 4, 2009.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://movies.rediff.com/report/2009/dec/07/tv-raju-srivastav-on-bigg-boss.htm|title=Was shocked when Tanaaz, Aditi pulled my pajamas|website=Rediff|date=Dec 7, 2009|first=Rajul|last=Hegde|access-date=2019-11-03}}</ref> He later participated in the comedy show ''[[Comedy Ka Maha Muqabala]]''.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/entertainment/events/bangalore/Raju-Srivastav-tickles-the-funny-bone-at-Le-Meridien-Bangalore/articleshow/30159461.cms|title=Raju Srivastav tickles the funny bone at Le Meridien, Bangalore|website=The Times of India}}</ref> In 2013, Raju along with his wife participated in ''[[Nach Baliye]] season 6'', which is a couples dance show on [[StarPlus]]. He has also appeared on ''[[Comedy Nights with Kapil]]''.

He also appeared in a show called ''[[Mazaak Mazaak Mein]]'' a.k.a. 'The Indian Mazaak League'. It was a stand-up comedy show which aired on [[Life OK]]. Popular cricketers [[Harbhajan Singh]] and [[Shoaib Akhtar]] were the judges of the show.

===Political career===
The [[Samajwadi Party]] fielded Srivastava from [[Kanpur (Lok Sabha constituency)|Kanpur]] for the [[2014 Lok Sabha election]].<ref>{{cite news|url=http://archive.indianexpress.com/news/akhilesh-yadav-turns-to-comedy-fields-raju-srivastava-from-kanpur-in-lok-sabha-election/1074076/ |title=Akhilesh Yadav turns to comedy, fields Raju Srivastava from Kanpur in Lok Sabha election |publisher=Indian Express |date=14 February 2013}}</ref> But on 11 March 2014, Srivastava returned the ticket, saying he was not getting enough support from the local units of the party.<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.thehindu.com/news/national/other-states/comedian-raju-srivastava-returns-sp-lok-sabha-ticket/article5773665.ece |title=Comedian Raju Srivastava returns SP Lok Sabha ticket |publisher=The Hindu |date=11 March 2014}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.newindianexpress.com/nation/2014/mar/11/Comedian-Raju-Srivastava-Returns-SP-Lok-Sabha-Ticket-585004.html|title=Comedian Raju Srivastava Returns SP Lok Sabha Ticket|website=The New Indian Express}}</ref> After that, he joined [[Bhartiya Janta Party]] on 19 March 2014.<ref>{{cite news|url=http://zeenews.india.com/news/nation/jagdambika-pal-comedian-raju-srivastava-join-bjp_918850.html |title=Jagdambika Pal, comedian Raju Srivastava join BJP, endorse Narendra Modi |publisher=Zee News |date=19 March 2014 |accessdate=19 March 2014}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://ibnlive.in.com/news/bjp-is-future-of-indian-politics-says-raju-srivastava/458907-3.html|title=News18.com: CNN-News18 Breaking News India, Latest News Headlines, Live News Updates|website=News18}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://indianexpress.com/article/india/politics/jagdambika-pal-artiste-raju-srivastava-join-bjp/|title=Jagdambika Pal, artiste Raju Srivastava join BJP|date=19 March 2014}}</ref>

Prime Minister [[Narendra Modi]] nominated him to be part of the [[Swachh Bharat Abhiyan]].<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.newindianexpress.com/entertainment/hindi/2017/oct/25/raju-srivastav-files-complaint-against-using-his-image-in-anti-bjp-message-1682539.html|title=Raju Srivastav files complaint against using his image in anti-BJP message|website=The New Indian Express|access-date=2019-11-03}}</ref> Since then he has been promoting cleanliness through his events in different cities. He has made various music videos for promoting cleanliness. He has also shot various TV commercials and social service message video for Swacha Bharat Abhiyaan.<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.newindianexpress.com/entertainment/hindi/2017/oct/25/raju-srivastav-files-complaint-against-using-his-image-in-anti-bjp-message-1682539.html|title=Raju Srivastav files complaint against using his image in anti-BJP message|website=The New Indian Express|date=25 October 2017|access-date=2019-11-03}}</ref>

